00:24:27,421 --> 00:24:29,721
"Colored Ball"

439
00:24:29,721 --> 00:24:31,321
The evidence is sweet honey.

440
00:24:31,321 --> 00:24:33,721
-But meat and potatoes... -Shouldn't be cooked too sweet.

